---
layout: base.njk
title: Reading
---

<h1>Reading</h1>

<p>I'm trying to keep track of things I liked reading this year.{% if reading.latestMonth %} Here's what I enjoyed reading most in {{ reading.latestMonth }}.{% endif %}</p>

{% set publicationTypes = ["Substack", "Newspaper"] %}
{% set articles = [] %}
{% set publications = [] %}
{% for item in reading.items %}
  {% if item.type in publicationTypes %}
    {% set _ = publications.push(item) %}
  {% else %}
    {% set _ = articles.push(item) %}
  {% endif %}
{% endfor %}

{% if articles | length > 0 %}
<section>
  <h2>Articles</h2>
  <ul class="reading-list">
  {% for item in articles %}
    <li class="reading-item">
      <span class="reading-name">{% if item.link %}<a href="{{ item.link }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ item.name }}</a>{% else %}{{ item.name }}{% endif %}</span>
      {% if item.date %}<span class="reading-date">{{ item.date }}</span>{% endif %}
    </li>
  {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</section>
{% endif %}

{% if publications | length > 0 %}
<section>
  <h2>Publications I Like</h2>
  <ul class="reading-list">
  {% for item in publications %}
    <li class="reading-item">
      <span class="reading-name">{% if item.link %}<a href="{{ item.link }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ item.name }}</a>{% else %}{{ item.name }}{% endif %}</span>
    </li>
  {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</section>
{% endif %}

<hr class="section-divider">

<h1>Books</h1>

<p>I also love books — mostly fiction, historical fiction, and the occasional sci-fi. I'm always on the hunt for a good recommendation. This is pulled automatically from <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/68621097-abby-krishnan">my Goodreads</a>.</p>

{% if goodreads.currentlyReading.length > 0 %}
<section>
  <h2>Currently Reading</h2>
  <ul class="book-list">
  {% for book in goodreads.currentlyReading %}
    <li class="book-item">
      <span class="book-title">{{ book.title }}</span>
      <span class="book-author">by {{ book.author }}</span>
    </li>
  {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</section>
{% endif %}

<section>
  <h2>Recently Read</h2>
  <ul class="book-list">
  {% for book in goodreads.read %}
    <li class="book-item">
      <span class="book-title">{{ book.title }}</span>
      <span class="book-author">by {{ book.author }}</span>
      {% if book.rating > 0 %}
      <span class="book-rating">
        {% for i in range(0, book.rating) %}★{% endfor %}{% for i in range(book.rating, 5) %}☆{% endfor %}
      </span>
      {% endif %}
    </li>
  {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</section>
